== 評價 ==
此部電影上映後得到普遍好評，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]有87%的新鮮度。英國《[[衛報|衛報]]》評價[[茱蒂·丹契|茱蒂·丹契]]與[[凱特·布蘭琪|凱特·布蘭琪]]對此部電影起到了巨大的作用。美國媒體也給予好評，《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》評價此片「拍出性感、憧憬的情愫，如電影《致命的吸引力》（''Fatal Attraction''）」<ref>{{cite news |title=Judi Dench puts the chill in 'Notes On a Scandal' thriller - The Boston Globe |url=https://www.boston.com/movies/display?display=movie&id=9123 |accessdate=2022-01-18 |work=www.boston.com |language=en |archive-date=2009-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090918015232/http://www.boston.com/movies/display?display=movie&id=9123 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=NOTES ON A SCANDAL: 4 STARS « Richard Crouse |url=https://richardcrouse.ca/notes-on-a-scandal-4-stars/ |accessdate=2022-01-18 |work=richardcrouse.ca |archive-date=2022-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220118230937/https://richardcrouse.ca/notes-on-a-scandal-4-stars/ }}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》影評人[[羅傑·艾伯特|羅傑·艾伯特]]表示，「[[茱蒂·丹契|茱蒂·丹契]]與[[凱特·布蘭琪|凱特·布蘭琪]]兩人扣人心弦的對手戲表現或許會成為2006年度最令人印象深刻的演出。」<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2007/feb/02/drama.periodandhistorical|title=Notes on a Scandal|date=2 February 2007|accessdate=22 August 2009|work=The Guardian|location=UK|last=Bradshaw|first=Peter|archive-date=2009-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028043512/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2007/feb/02/drama.periodandhistorical}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://uk.rottentomatoes.com/m/notes_on_a_scandal/?critic=creamcrop|title=Notes on a Scandal (2006)|accessdate=22 August 2009|work=Rotten Tomatoes''|archive-date=2013-02-01|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130201171517/http://uk.rottentomatoes.com/m/notes_on_a_scandal/?critic=creamcrop|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

